title: Livin' in the '80s (Q Magazine Promo Cassette) [1994]
description:
"14 tracks from Top of the Pops"

This Compilation Cassette Album was released in 1994 by Virgin Records Ltd. Was given away with Q Magazine, November 1994 Number 98 & UK Gold - Not for resale.

It was released in conjunction with re-run of 'Top of the Pops' on UK Gold, every weekday at 17:40hrs & 22:30hrs. 

(This is not a rip of the cassette but a recreation of the compilation with the same tracks of varying bitrates, from 128-320)
